{"title":"车间主任也要管思想","authors":["子曰"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":10,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"车间主任也要管思想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二车间主任林洪轩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他工作细心苦在先。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"计划掌握得很牢靠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成本降低无数元。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林主任一心搞生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘了业务组之间闹意见。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管业务也得管思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双管齐下才圆满。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五三工厂　子曰"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}